## 💡 Logic Building Practice

### Remove Duplicates from a List

```python
nums = [1, 2, 2, 3, 4, 4, 5]

unique_nums = list(set(nums))
print(unique_nums)
```

### Find Common Elements

```python
a = {1, 2, 3, 4}
b = {3, 4, 5, 6}

print(a.intersection(b))
```

### Find Unique Elements Between Two Lists

```python
a = {1, 2, 3}
b = {3, 4, 5}

print(a.symmetric_difference(b))
